--></div><div class="infinite-carousel-item" data-v-b834ddec><!--[--><img src="https://cdn.navixy.com/logo_nestle_0e313338a3.svg" width="105" height="60" data-v-3191e575><!--]--></div><div class="infinite-carousel-item" data-v-b834ddec><!--[--><img src="https://cdn.navixy.com/logo_amazon_e248d33171.svg" width="105" height="60" data-v-3191e575><!--]--></div><div class="infinite-carousel-item" data-v-b834ddec><!--[--><img src="https://cdn.navixy.com/logo_dhl_274e943883.svg" width="105" height="60" data-v-3191e575><!--]--></div><div class="infinite-carousel-item" data-v-b834ddec><!--[--><img src="https://cdn.navixy.com/logo_toyota_e96f263fc7.svg" width="105" height="60" data-v-3191e575><!--]--></div><!--]--></div></div><div class="modal-component-container" data-v-3191e575 data-v-678698b6><span></span></div></section><section class="solutions" data-v-69da5266 data-v-bf0f434d><div class="solutions-container" data-v-bf0f434d><div class="title" data-v-bf0f434d data-v-2d3b5fba><h1 class="black" data-v-2d3b5fba>Build innovative GPS and telematics solutions</h1><h3 class="black" data-v-2d3b5fba>Navixy simplifies the creation and scaling of high-performance GPS and telematics applications, equipping integrators and developers with powerful solutions and tools to tackle unique business challenges.</h3></div><div class="solutions-wrapper" data-v-bf0f434d><div class="tabs" data-v-bf0f434d data-v-31c4583b><div class="tabs-menu" data-v-31c4583b><!--[--><button class="tabs-menu-selected tabs-menu-label" data-v-31c4583b>Location tracking</button><button class="tabs-menu-label" data-v-31c4583b>Vehicle telemetry</button><button class="tabs-menu-label" data-v-31c4583b>Workforce management</button><button class="tabs-menu-label" data-v-31c4583b>Data solutions</button><!--]--><div class="tabs-menu-indicator" style="left:0px;width:0px;" data-v-31c4583b></div></div><div class="tabs-content-wrapper" data-v-31c4583b><!--[--><div style="" class="active tabs-content" data-v-31c4583b><div class="tabs-content-text" data-v-31c4583b><div class="tabs-content-text-label" data-v-31c4583b>Enhance visibility with real-time location tracking and advanced mapping tools, including POIs, geofences, and custom map layers. Monitor vehicles, staff, and cargo with remote control capabilities for security and efficiency.</div><a class="tabs-content-text-link" href="/asset-gps-tracking/features/" target="_self" data-v-31c4583b>Learn more</a></div><div class="tabs-content-image" data-v-31c4583b><img src="https://cdn.navixy.com/slider_gps_asset_tracking_2x_988efb5727.webp" alt="Location tracking" data-v-31c4583b></div></div><div style="display:none;" class="tabs-content" data-v-31c4583b><div class="tabs-content-text" data-v-31c4583b><div class="tabs-content-text-label" data-v-31c4583b>Leverage advanced telemetry with real-time visualization to optimize fleet performance and reduce risks. Improve eco-driving, enhance safety with video telematics and ADAS, streamline maintenance, and prevent fuel fraud.</div><a class="tabs-content-text-link" href="/fleet-management/features/" target="_self" data-v-31c4583b>Learn more</a></div><div class="tabs-content-image" data-v-31c4583b><img src="https://cdn.navixy.com/slider_fleet_management_2x_effd5019d6.webp" alt="Vehicle telemetry" data-v-31c4583b></div></div><div style="display:none;" class="tabs-content" data-v-31c4583b><div class="tabs-content-text" data-v-31c4583b><div class="tabs-content-text-label" data-v-31c4583b>Digitize job dispatch, reporting, and communication between field staff and office teams. Enhance coordination and efficiency of business operations with route optimization, electronic forms, and real-time monitoring.</div><a class="tabs-content-text-link" href="/field-service/features/" target="_self" data-v-31c4583b>Learn more</a></div><div class="tabs-content-image" data-v-31c4583b><img src="https://cdn.navixy.com/slider_field_service_2x_f2890fcb2f.webp" alt="Workforce management" data-v-31c4583b></div></div><div style="display:none;" class="tabs-content" data-v-31c4583b><div class="tabs-content-text" data-v-31c4583b><div class="tabs-content-text-label" data-v-31c4583b>Ingest raw data for troubleshooting and analysis, transform it with expression language for advanced calculations and modifications, and seamlessly transmit processed data to visualization tools and external systems.</div><a class="tabs-content-text-link" href="/iot-logic/" target="_self" data-v-31c4583b>Learn more</a></div><div class="tabs-content-image" data-v-31c4583b><img src="https://cdn.navixy.com/slider_iot_2x_3900e54357.webp" alt="Data solutions" data-v-31c4583b></div></div><!--]--></div></div></div></div></section><section class="customers" data-v-69da5266 data-v-0e4dd2b8><div class="customers-container" data-v-0e4dd2b8><div class="title" data-v-0e4dd2b8 data-v-2d3b5fba><h1 class="white" data-v-2d3b5fba>Meet the companies who build with Navixy</h1><h3 class="white" data-v-2d3b5fba>Together with our global network of integrators and developers, we have successfully delivered thousands of projects from startups to enterprises, solving industry-specific challenges.</h3></div><div class="customers-cards" data-v-0e4dd2b8><!--[--><div class="card" data-v-0e4dd2b8 data-v-83675504><div class="card-top" data-v-83675504><div class="card-image" style="background-image:url(https://cdn.navixy.com/cusromer_anthony_a3d9495d21.webp);" data-v-83675504></div><div data-v-83675504></div><div class="card-author" data-v-83675504>Anthony, CEO and Co-founder </div><div class="card-logo" data-v-83675504><img src="https://cdn.navixy.com/track_nroute_51c557c2a3.webp" alt="Track-n-Route Company logo" data-v-83675504></div></div><div class="card-text" data-v-83675504>&quot;Navixy gives us flexibility and robustness to provide a complete all-in-one solution to any business, regardless of their sphere and location.&quot; </div></div><div class="card" data-v-0e4dd2b8 data-v-83675504><div class="card-top" data-v-83675504><div class="card-image" style="background-image:url(https://cdn.navixy.com/Bodo_dark_8b2738077c.webp);" data-v-83675504></div><div data-v-83675504></div><div class="card-author" data-v-83675504>Bodo Erken, CEO</div><div class="card-logo" data-v-83675504><img src="https://cdn.navixy.com/Trackerrando_de_logo_560fc02e0e.webp" alt="null" data-v-83675504></div></div><div class="card-text" data-v-83675504>&quot;We have been offering Navixy as a solution to our customers for over 5 years. The associated advantages such as user-friendliness, stability and fast service response are the guarantee of our success.&quot;</div></div><div class="card" data-v-0e4dd2b8 data-v-83675504><div class="card-top" data-v-83675504><div class="card-image" style="background-image:url(https://cdn.navixy.com/cusromer_danny_bc84e47b3f.webp);" data-v-83675504></div><div data-v-83675504></div><div class="card-author" data-v-83675504>Danny, Chief Technical Officer</div><div class="card-logo" data-v-83675504><img src="https://cdn.navixy.com/thaisoft_0e11b48db5.webp" alt="ThaiSoft Company logo" data-v-83675504></div></div><div class="card-text" data-v-83675504>&quot;Our overall experience with Navixy has been great. The features and the support helped our company expand in many ways, and we look forward to working with them for years to come.&quot;</div></div><!--]--></div><!----></div></section><section class="achieve" data-v-69da5266 data-v-ee844cf5><div class="achieve-container" data-v-ee844cf5><div class="achieve-title" data-v-ee844cf5><div class="title" data-v-ee844cf5 data-v-2d3b5fba><h1 class="black" data-v-2d3b5fba>Telematics platform to innovate and scale globally</h1><h3 class="black" data-v-2d3b5fba>Navixy makes building, deploying, and scaling GPS and telematics applications easy and flexible. With 20+ years of expertise, we ensure reliable performance and ongoing innovation.</h3></div><a class="element-btn element-btn--azure element-btn--large" href="#" target="_self" data-v-ee844cf5 data-v-d22aa132><!----><!--[-->Get started<!--]--></a></div><div class="achieve-counters" data-v-ee844cf5><!--[--><div class="achieve-counters-item" data-v-ee844cf5><h5 data-v-ee844cf5>800K+</h5><p data-v-ee844cf5>online assets</p></div><div class="achieve-counters-item" data-v-ee844cf5><h5 data-v-ee844cf5>10K+</h5><p data-v-ee844cf5>completed projects</p></div><div class="achieve-counters-item" data-v-ee844cf5><h5 data-v-ee844cf5>130+</h5><p data-v-ee844cf5>customer countries</p></div><div class="achieve-counters-item" data-v-ee844cf5><h5 data-v-ee844cf5>99.9%</h5><p data-v-ee844cf5>historical uptime</p></div><!--]--></div><div class="achieve-cards" data-v-ee844cf5><!--[--><div class="achieve-cards-card" data-v-ee844cf5><div class="achieve-cards-card-image" data-v-ee844cf5><img src="https://cdn.navixy.com/high_perfomance_icon_303da98a08.svg" width="80" height="81" data-v-ee844cf5></div><div class="achieve-cards-card-title" data-v-ee844cf5>High-performance tracking</div><div class="achieve-cards-card-text" data-v-ee844cf5>Navixy combines modern technologies with an intuitive design, supporting real-time tracking of up to 25,000 assets in a single account.</div></div><div class="achieve-cards-card" data-v-ee844cf5><div class="achieve-cards-card-image" data-v-ee844cf5><img src="https://cdn.navixy.com/no_code_icon_066c3b0ea7.svg" width="80" height="81" data-v-ee844cf5></div><div class="achieve-cards-card-title" data-v-ee844cf5>No-code customization</div><div class="achieve-cards-card-text" data-v-ee844cf5>Navixy telematics PaaS enables businesses to personalize UI, integrate third-party apps, and customize telematics data processing.</div></div><div class="achieve-cards-card" data-v-ee844cf5><div class="achieve-cards-card-image" data-v-ee844cf5><img src="https://cdn.navixy.com/support_icon_93cd385cc0.svg" width="80" height="81" data-v-ee844cf5></div><div class="achieve-cards-card-title" data-v-ee844cf5>Engineering support</div><div class="achieve-cards-card-text" data-v-ee844cf5>Navixy delivers top-tier technical and solution engineering support with a 98% satisfaction rate, enabling businesses to optimize operations.</div></div><div class="achieve-cards-card" data-v-ee844cf5><div class="achieve-cards-card-image" data-v-ee844cf5><img src="https://cdn.navixy.com/data_orchestration_icon_584b774daa.svg" width="80" height="81" data-v-ee844cf5></div><div class="achieve-cards-card-title" data-v-ee844cf5>Data orchestration</div><div class="achieve-cards-card-text" data-v-ee844cf5>Navixy offers advanced tools and solutions for seamless ingestion, decoding, transformation, and visualization of telematics and GPS data.</div></div><div class="achieve-cards-card" data-v-ee844cf5><div class="achieve-cards-card-image" data-v-ee844cf5><img src="https://cdn.navixy.com/ap_I_centric_icon_104c4ab91d.svg" width="80" height="81" data-v-ee844cf5></div><div class="achieve-cards-card-title" data-v-ee844cf5>API-centric architecture</div><div class="achieve-cards-card-text" data-v-ee844cf5>Navixy provides powerful and easy-to-use APIs to streamline development and save engineering time for building scalable telematics solutions.</div></div><div class="achieve-cards-card" data-v-ee844cf5><div class="achieve-cards-card-image" data-v-ee844cf5><img src="https://cdn.navixy.com/telematics_superapp_icon_2ce33fb727.svg" width="80" height="81" data-v-ee844cf5></div><div class="achieve-cards-card-title" data-v-ee844cf5>Telematics superapp</div><div class="achieve-cards-card-text" data-v-ee844cf5>Navixy’s iOS and Android apps empower field teams with real-time workforce management, ensuring seamless operations on the go.</div></div><!--]--></div></div><div class="modal-component-container" data-v-ee844cf5 data-v-678698b6><span></span></div></section><section class="learn" data-v-69da5266 data-v-b60d5d52><div class="learn-container" data-v-b60d5d52><div class="learn-content" data-v-b60d5d52><div class="learn-title" data-v-b60d5d52><h1 data-v-b60d5d52>Explore Navixy</h1><p data-v-b60d5d52>Learn more about Navixy on our YouTube channel. From step-by-step guides and feature highlights to industry insights, our videos help you discover the full potential of the Navixy telematics platform.</p><a class="element-btn element-btn--transparent element-btn--large" href="https://www.youtube.com/@Navixy" target="_self" data-v-b60d5d52 data-v-d22aa132><!----><!--[-->Watch more<!--]--></a></div><div class="learn-video" data-v-b60d5d52><div class="learn-video-preview" data-v-b60d5d52><div class="learn-video-preview-image" data-v-b60d5d52><img src="https://vumbnail.com/866284060.jpg" alt="What is Navixy: advanced telematics software" data-v-b60d5d52></div><div class="learn-video-preview-play" data-v-b60d5d52><svg viewBox="0 0 54 54" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" data-v-b60d5d52><g id="button" data-v-b60d5d52><rect x="0.0664062" y="0.078125" width="52.9495" height="52.9495" rx="26.4748" fill="white" data-v-b60d5d52></rect><path id="Vector" d="M38.7912 26.9973C38.7912 27.4879 38.5306 27.9416 38.1069 28.1888L21.5552 37.8439C21.1286 38.0927 20.6015 38.0945 20.1733 37.8484C19.745 37.6025 19.481 37.1464 19.481 36.6524V17.3422C19.481 16.8483 19.745 16.3921 20.1733 16.1461C20.6015 15.9002 21.1286 15.9019 21.5552 16.1508L38.1069 25.8059C38.5306 26.053 38.7912 26.5067 38.7912 26.9973Z" fill="#007AD2" data-v-b60d5d52></path></g></svg></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="marketplace" data-v-69da5266 data-v-2855f7b8><div class="marketplace-container" data-v-2855f7b8><div class="marketplace-title" data-v-2855f7b8><div class="title" data-v-2855f7b8 data-v-2d3b5fba><h1 class="black" data-v-2d3b5fba> Expand Navixy with Marketplace solutions</h1><h3 class="black" data-v-2d3b5fba>Discover, test, and deploy custom-built GPS and telematics apps from the developer community, along  with ready-made solutions from specialized partners and Navixy.</h3></div><a class="element-btn element-btn--azure element-btn--large" href="https://marketplace.navixy.com/" target="_blank" data-v-2855f7b8 data-v-d22aa132><!----><!--[-->Visit Marketplace<!--]--></a></div></div><div data-v-2855f7b8></div><span data-v-2855f7b8></span></section><section class="blog" data-v-69da5266 data-v-57390833><div class="blog-container" data-v-57390833><div class="blog-title" data-v-57390833><div class="title" data-v-57390833 data-v-2d3b5fba><h1 class="black" data-v-2d3b5fba>Stay ahead with the latest news and trends</h1><h3 class="black" data-v-2d3b5fba>Keep up with the latest Navixy updates and telematics news. Gain insights into emerging technologies, industry innovations, and best practices.</h3></div><a class="element-btn element-btn--azure element-btn--large" href="/blog" target="_self" data-v-57390833 data-v-d22aa132><!----><!--[-->Explore blog<!--]--></a></div><div class="blog-cards" data-v-57390833><!--[--><div class="blog-cards-card" data-v-57390833><div class="blog-cards-card-image" data-v-57390833><img src="https://cdn.navixy.com/user_applications_1400x732_ca3d7be523.webp" data-v-57390833></div><div class="blog-cards-card-info" data-v-57390833><div class="blog-cards-card-info-main" data-v-57390833><h3 data-v-57390833>Make Navixy work for you: Introducing User Applications</h3><p data-v-57390833>Navixy’s new User Applications feature allows you to embed custom web apps directly within the platform. Whether it’s fleet analytics, compliance tools, or industry-specific modules, this functionality empowers integrators to create tailored telematics solutions for their clients.…</p></div><a href="/blog/make-navixy-work-for-you/" data-v-57390833>Learn more</a></div></div><div class="blog-cards-card" data-v-57390833><div class="blog-cards-card-image" data-v-57390833><img src="https://cdn.navixy.com/ngp_data_exchange_1_1400x732_5fcb17e657.webp" data-v-57390833></div><div class="blog-cards-card-info" data-v-57390833><div class="blog-cards-card-info-main" data-v-57390833><h3 data-v-57390833>Introducing NGP: A new standard for telematics data exchange</h3><p data-v-57390833>We&#39;re introducing the Navixy Generic Protocol (NGP) — our answer to the fragmentation challenge in the telematics industry. We’ll explore how the Navixy Generic Protocol transforms telematics, how it works, and the ways it can benefit your operations.…</p></div><a href="/blog/introducing-ngp/" data-v-57390833>Learn more</a></div></div><div class="blog-cards-card" data-v-57390833><div class="blog-cards-card-image" data-v-57390833><img src="https://cdn.navixy.com/featured_image_1400x732_72937dcf91.webp" data-v-57390833></div><div class="blog-cards-card-info" data-v-57390833><div class="blog-cards-card-info-main" data-v-57390833><h3 data-v-57390833>Enhancing public transportation with automatic passenger counter solution</h3><p data-v-57390833>Navixy’s automatic passenger counter solutions, powered by advanced sensors like the ASPC102, enable transit operators to optimize routes, improve occupancy rates, and reduce operational costs. Learn how real-time passenger data can enhance efficiency and customer satisfaction.…</p></div><a href="/blog/enhancing-public-transportation/" data-v-57390833>Learn more</a></div></div><!--]--></div></div></section><div data-v-69da5266></div></main><footer class="footer" data-v-e12afa74><div class="footer-container" data-v-e12afa74><section class="footer-menu" data-v-e12afa74 data-v-73637103><div class="footer-menu-container" data-v-73637103><!--[--><div class="footer-menu-column" data-v-73637103><h4 data-v-73637103>Platform</h4><!--[--><a href="/platform/datahub/" class="" data-v-73637103>DataHub</a><a href="/iot-logic" data-v-73637103>IoT Logic</a><a href="/platform/live-view-suite/overview/" class="" data-v-73637103>LiveView Suite</a><a href="/features/mobile-apps" data-v-73637103>X-GPS Mobile</a><a href="/features/admin-panel" data-v-73637103>Admin panel</a><a href="/devices" data-v-73637103>GPS &amp; IoT devices</a><a href="https://www.navixy.com/docs/developers/" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-v-7363710